summary: BittensorVM - BittensorVM marks a significant milestone in the evolution of Layer 2 solutions, elevating the Ethereum ecosystem to new heights of scalability, security, and operational efficiency. By seamlessly integrating cutting-edge rollup technology, smart AI through the Bittensor Network and TAO AI, alongside the revolutionary TENSOR AI MEV (Miner Extractable Value) protection, BittensorVM sets itself apart as a beacon of innovation in the decentralized finance (DeFi) and application space.
